Company Overview
Beach Point Capital Management LP is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides sits services to public and corporate pension funds, endowments, state or municipal government entities, foreign pension schemes, individuals, companies, corporate plans, endowments, trusts, foundations, charitable organizations, and other investment funds. It also manages client specific portfolios. The firm invests in fixed income and public equity markets across the globe. It diversifies its investments across bonds, corporate loans, distressed debt, convertible notes, floating rate bonds, and DIP loans. The firm combines value, special situations, and opportunistic strategies to make it...
Beach Point Capital Management LP is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides sits services to public and corporate pension funds, endowments, state or municipal government entities, foreign pension schemes, individuals, companies, corporate plans, endowments, trusts, foundations, charitable organizations, and other investment funds. It also manages client specific portfolios. The firm invests in fixed income and public equity markets across the globe. It diversifies its investments across bonds, corporate loans, distressed debt, convertible notes, floating rate bonds, and DIP loans. The firm combines value, special situations, and opportunistic strategies to make its investments. It employs fundamental and technical analysis to create its investments portfolios. The firm conducts in-house research for investments. Beach Point Capital Management LP was founded on January 1, 2009 and is based in Los Angeles, California; with additional offices in New York, New York; and London, United Kingdom.
