    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 87.33%. Beach Point Capital Management's largest holding is MGM Resorts International, Inc. with shares held of 2,546,314.  Beach Point Capital Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 28 13Fs and  2 13D/G filings in our database for Beach Point Capital Management. 
                                           






