ShareOverviewBeach Point Capital Management, LP is a registered investment advisory firm located in Santa Monica, California. The firm manages 64 accounts totaling an estimated $13,032,506,050 USD in assets under management. Its operations include 78 employees and is categorized as providing investment advisory services to 100 clients. Many more details can be found below. You can also click here to see a list of all 99 investment advisors located in Santa Monica, California.
